{{Infobox artwork | image_file = Personnage gothique.JPG | painting_alignment = Front | image_size = 250px | title = Personnage Gothique, Oiseau-Eclair | alt = | other_language_1 = | other_title_1 = | other_language_2 = | other_title_2 = | artist = Joan Miró | year = 1974 | type = sculpture | height_metric = 450.2 | width_metric = 200.0 | length_metric = 160.0 | height_imperial = 14 | height_inch = {{frac|9|1|4}} | width_imperial = 6 | width_inch = {{frac|6|3|4}} | length_imperial = 5 | length_inch = 3 | metric_unit = cm | imperial_unit = ft | city = Washington, D.C. | museum = [[National Gallery of Art Sculpture Garden]] | coordinates = {{coord|38|53|30.48|N|77|1|24.25|W|type:landmark_region:US_dim:1}} | owner = National Gallery of Art }}
'''''Personnage Gothique, Oiseau-Eclair''''' is a bronze sculpture by [[Joan Miró]].<ref>[http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=FX01327960E26.20894&menu=search&aspect=Keyword&npp=50&ipp=20&spp=20&profile=ariall&ri=21&source=%7E%21siartinventories&index=.GW&term=Personnage+Gothique%2C+Oiseau-Eclair&aspect=Keyword&x=9&y=11#focus "Personnage Gothique, Oiseau-Eclair, (sculpture)"]. ''SIRIS''</ref>
It was created in 1974, and cast in 1977. It is in the [[National Gallery of Art Sculpture Garden]], Washington, USA.<ref>http://www.nga.gov/feature/sculpturegarden/sculpture/sculpture2.shtm</ref>
